{"tid":1267544,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【蘋果獨家】港鐵主席馬時亨免費坐呂志和私人飛機兼有女同遊 嘉華今年投得康城站用地","createTime":"2019-06-30T02:49:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T02:21:12.000Z","uid":48083,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"964777c0c34c37ad7b6f5fadad786cd91c459523","tid":1267544,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T02:49:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4gD03cF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4gD03cF.png&h=fb0e23cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n明日卸任的港鐵主席馬時亨被揭發利益衝突醜聞。《蘋果》獲悉，馬時亨與嘉華國際主席呂志和去年多次聯袂乘搭私人飛機出外旅遊，而且有數名女性陪同。消息指，馬時亨外遊數次均無付費。<br />\n<br />\n去年呂志和與馬時亨外遊後，今年嘉華集團合組財團便以30.5億元投得港鐵康城發展項目地皮。有立法會議員質疑港鐵作為公共機構，主席應保持獨立角色，接受款待亦需有清晰申報，否則遇利益衝突時，有可能構成公職人員行為失當。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵回覆《蘋果》指，馬時亨並非港鐵僱員，又指港鐵是上市商業機構而非公營機構，「公司主席不屬於公職人員」，只需循上市公司規則申報。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8Nmh5q7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8Nmh5q7.png&h=4d27a54a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qWuLuSO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqWuLuSO.png&h=e003413e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OdGeocP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOdGeocP.png&h=84183a56&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DT8Hw6a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDT8Hw6a.png&h=9254a607&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EYi03cR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEYi03cR.png&h=0f9e75a7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CRvZzjx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCRvZzjx.png&h=7ad8d92c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P66NJcT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP66NJcT.png&h=ea843390&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xesdDMe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxesdDMe.png&h=71972313&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190630/59771340?itm_campaign=hkad_internal_link&amp;itm_medium=internal&amp;itm_source=hkad_mweb&amp;itm_content=internal_link_1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190630%2F59771340%3Fitm_campaign%3Dhkad_internal_link%26itm_medium%3Dinternal%26itm_source%3Dhkad_mweb%26itm_content%3Dinternal_link_1&d=FGEw0iwwiNltpS2R1LMyGoE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=708c7bd6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190630%2F59771340%3Fitm_campaign%3Dhkad_internal_link%26itm_medium%3Dinternal%26itm_source%3Dhkad_mweb%26itm_content%3Dinternal_link_1&h=0491bca1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190630/59771340?itm_campaign=hkad_internal_link&amp;itm_medium=internal&amp;itm_source=hkad_mweb&amp;itm_content=internal_link_1</a>"},{"pid":"2200b9ac0e34ba4e353312079b42a0728bc3f154","tid":1267544,"uid":48083,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T02:50:44.000Z","msg":"記得訂閱蘋果，支持佢繼續發掘真相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b1d8ea6f38bdba51fbcb2d43189f811b0c2f4ec","tid":1267544,"uid":54455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T02:51:40.000Z","msg":"有人有力咁"},{"pid":"9ff7f8c678ca66a88a7e2a64345104b19587f4a0","tid":1267544,"uid":54455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b1d8ea6f38bdba51fbcb2d43189f811b0c2f4ec","tid":1267544,"uid":54455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-